desc: An eccentric genius forms an international network of super-geniuses to act as the last line of defense against the complicated threats of the modern world.

title: Psych
desc: A novice sleuth is hired by the police after he cons them into thinking he has psychic powers which help solve crimes. With the assistance of his reluctant best friend, the duo take on a series of complicated cases.

title: A Bad Moms Christmas
desc: As their own mothers drop in unexpectedly, our three under-appreciated and over-burdened moms rebel against the challenges and expectations of the Super Bowl for mothers: Christmas.

title: Cars 3
desc: Lightning McQueen sets out to prove to a new generation of racers that he's still the best race car in the world.

title: Money Heist
desc: A group of very peculiar robbers have assaulted the Factory of Moneda and Timbre to carry out the most perfect robbery in the history of Spain and taking home 2,400 million euros.

title: House of Cards
desc: A Congressman works with his equally conniving wife to exact revenge on the people who betrayed him.

title: The Originals
desc: A family of power-hungry thousand year old vampires look to take back the city that they built and dominate all those who have done them wrong.

title: Sicario
desc: An idealistic FBI agent is enlisted by a government task force to aid in the escalating war against drugs at the border area between the U.S. and Mexico.

title: Home Again
desc: Life for a single mom in Los Angeles takes an unexpected turn when she allows three young guys to move in with her.

title: Jeepers Creepers III
desc: Sheriff Dan Tashtego and a team of creeper hunters enlist the help of officer Davis Tubbs to help stop the monster's eating spree.

title: The Good Place
desc: A woman struggles to define what it means to be good.

title: How to Get Away with Murder
desc: A group of ambitious law students and their brilliant criminal defense professor become involved in a twisted murder plot that promises to change the course of their lives.

title: The Florida Project
desc: Set over one summer, the film follows precocious six-year-old Moonee as she courts mischief and adventure with her ragtag playmates and bonds with her rebellious but caring mother, all while living in the shadows of Disney World.

title: Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire
desc: A young wizard finds himself competing in a hazardous tournament between rival schools of magic, but he is distracted by recurring nightmares.

title: Mad Max: Fury Road
desc: A woman rebels against a tyrannical ruler in postapocalyptic Australia in search for her home-land with the help of a group of female prisoners, a psychotic worshipper, and a drifter named Max.

title: The LEGO Batman Movie
desc: A cooler-than-ever Bruce Wayne must deal with the usual suspects as they plan to rule Gotham City, while discovering that he has accidentally adopted a teenage orphan who wishes to become his sidekick.

desc: Follows District 21 of the Chicago Police Department, which is made up of two distinctly different groups: the uniformed cops and the Intelligence Unit.

title: Hidden Figures
desc: The story of a team of female African-American mathematicians who served a vital role in NASA during the early years of the U.S. space program.

title: Transformers: The Last Knight
desc: Autobots and Decepticons are at war, with humans on the sidelines. Optimus Prime is gone. The key to saving our future lies buried in the secrets of the past, in the hidden history of Transformers on Earth.

title: The Great Gatsby
desc: A writer and wall street trader, Nick, finds himself drawn to the past and lifestyle of his millionaire neighbor, Jay Gatsby.

title: The Santa Clause 3: The Escape Clause
desc: Santa, aka Scott Calvin, is faced with double-duty: how to keep his new family happy, and how to stop Jack Frost from taking over Christmas.

title: Pretty Little Liars
desc: Four friends band together against an anonymous foe who threatens to reveal their darkest secrets, while also investigating the disappearance of their best friend.

title: Wonder Wheel
desc: On Coney Island in the 1950s, a lifeguard tells the story of a middle-aged carousel operator and his beleaguered wife.

title: Interstellar
desc: A team of explorers travel through a wormhole in space in an attempt to ensure humanity's survival.

title: The Fate of the Furious
desc: When a mysterious woman seduces Dom into the world of terrorism and a betrayal of those closest to him, the crew face trials that will test them as never before.

title: A Christmas Story Live!
desc: A live broadcast of the Broadway hit "A Christmas Story: The Musical" in which Ralphie wishes for nothing more than a Red Ryder BB Gun for Christmas.

title: A Christmas Prince
desc: When a reporter goes undercover as a tutor to get the inside scoop on a playboy prince, she gets tangled in some royal intrigue and ends up finding love - but will she be able to keep up her lie?

title: Despicable Me 3
desc: Gru meets his long-lost charming, cheerful, and more successful twin brother Dru who wants to team up with him for one last criminal heist.

title: NCIS: Los Angeles
desc: The Naval Criminal Investigation Service's Office of Special Projects takes on the undercover work and the hard to crack cases in LA. Key agents are G. Callen and Sam Hanna, streets kids risen through the ranks.

title: Blue Bloods
desc: Revolves around a family of New York cops.

title: Crooked House
desc: In Agatha Christie's most twisted tale, a spy-turned-private-detective is lured by his former lover to catch her grandfather's murderer before Scotland Yard exposes dark family secrets.

title: Teen Wolf
desc: A somewhat awkward teen is attacked by a werewolf and inherits the curse himself, as well as the enemies that come with it.

title: Bones
desc: Forensic anthropologist Dr. Temperance "Bones" Brennan and cocky F.B.I. Special Agent Seeley Booth build a team to investigate murders. Quite often, there isn't more to examine than rotten flesh or mere bones.

title: The Hateful Eight
desc: In the dead of a Wyoming winter, a bounty hunter and his prisoner find shelter in a cabin currently inhabited by a collection of nefarious characters.

title: Bob's Burgers
desc: Bob Belcher, along with his wife and 3 children, try to run their last hope of holding the family together, which is running Bob's dream restaurant.

title: Prison Break
desc: Due to a political conspiracy, an innocent man is sent to death row and his only hope is his brother, who makes it his mission to deliberately get himself sent to the same prison in order to break the both of them out, from the inside.

title: When Calls the Heart

title: The Dark Knight
desc: When the menace known as the Joker emerges from his mysterious past, he wreaks havoc and chaos on the people of Gotham, the Dark Knight must accept one of the greatest psychological and physical tests of his ability to fight injustice.

title: American Gods
desc: A recently released ex-convict named Shadow meets a mysterious man who calls himself "Wednesday" and who knows more than he first seems to about Shadow's life and past.

title: Downton Abbey
desc: A chronicle of the lives of the British aristocratic Crawley family and their servants in the early 20th Century.

title: El Chapo
desc: A look at the life of notorious drug kingpin, El Chapo, from his early days in the 1980s working for the Guadalajara Cartel, to his rise to power of during the '90s and his ultimate downfall in 2016.

title: Trolls
desc: After the Bergens invade Troll Village, Poppy, the happiest Troll ever born, and the curmudgeonly Branch set off on a journey to rescue her friends.

title: Deadpool
desc: A fast-talking mercenary with a morbid sense of humor is subjected to a rogue experiment that leaves him with accelerated healing powers and a quest for revenge.

title: Mad Men
desc: A drama about one of New York's most prestigious ad agencies at the beginning of the 1960s, focusing on one of the firm's most mysterious but extremely talented ad executives, Donald Draper.

title: Bleeding Steel
desc: Chan stars as a hardened special forces agent who fights to protect a young woman from a sinister criminal gang. At the same time he with feels a special connection to the young woman, like they met in a different life.
